{"tid":1382173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【閪門吹雪】近日香港部分地區空氣污染日益嚴重， 令人痛哭流涕","createTime":"2019-07-29T11:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T06:17:20.000Z","uid":259781,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9186debfbf0be7160124d7b7bee934591c611ca1","tid":1382173,"uid":259781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"聽講近日市區<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">市民吸煙嘅情況非常嚴重</span></strong>， 有好多平時唔食煙嘅居民，都不幸地中咗呢班煙民嘅二手煙， <span style=\"color: gold;\">而且有部分煙鏟愈食愈醇</span>， 令好多關心香港人健康嘅民間控煙辦成員痛哭流涕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有見及此， 就等我教大家用家用器具保護自己至關重要嘅肺部啦。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n秘訣就係喺香港隨處可見清潔工手中所攞嘅枯葉吹風機！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/DEWALT-DCBL720P1-Lithium-Brushless-Blower/dp/B00TL72F2E?ref_=fsclp_pl_dp_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDEWALT-DCBL720P1-Lithium-Brushless-Blower%2Fdp%2FB00TL72F2E%3Fref_%3Dfsclp_pl_dp_1&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiY%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=71977791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/DEWALT-DCBL720P1-Lithium-Brushless-Blower/dp/B00TL72F2E?ref_=fsclp_pl_dp_1</a><br />\n<br />\n就好似呢一款機咁，佢係用 20V 鋰電推動， 作用範圍十分可觀， 能夠有效對付大規模煙害， 只要搭配多幾部一齊使用， 就可以喺極短時間內淨化空氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3G3sVVG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3G3sVVG.jpg&h=d09a9745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請各位化身閪門吹雪， 積極推廣香港全面禁煙！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你係煙鏟， 好鍾意食煙都唔緊要， 只要確認周圍冇控煙辦就再玩得癲啲， 好似呢位外國仁兄咁與煙民同樂， <span style=\"color: purple;\">大玩煙霧瀰漫嘅公眾派對！</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/esTVyPFAM30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FesTVyPFAM30&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiY%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=273e23ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/esTVyPFAM30</a><br />\n<br />\n拿咁當然， 影片入面呢一類內容物呢， 就係犯法嘅， 但係水煙喺香港就好似好受歡迎， 如果有返三五十支充撐一下場面， 相信大家都可以有一個非常愉快嘅晚上。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Asmm0pf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAsmm0pf.jpg&h=2d5fec1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煙～繼續吹    不忍遠離<br />\n心裏極渴望    不用流淚望著你"},{"pid":"91cdb8f1e249a2aa3c51eb8b17ce2bc46c3636c8","tid":1382173,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e210430eab27635e0bc7cb401c8fa3ba6442a96a","tid":1382173,"uid":11970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"最後嗰句<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f10b6f010eae0e43af9130151254a92c675802f","tid":1382173,"uid":259781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:55:20.000Z","msg":"PUSHHHH"},{"pid":"2c1bad9f6b881a567d8f3166b357e4caeaf3fbd5","tid":1382173,"uid":269695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:50:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2646add0199bbd9fd5c3210d74107aa928b31ea0","tid":1382173,"uid":162969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"心裏極渴望 不用流淚望著你"}]}